    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of this car, from the flawless exterior paint and pristine interior upholstery to the meticulously maintained engine bay, reflects a level of care that is rarely seen. There are no scratches, dents, or mechanical issues to report; it runs perfectly and offers all the modern features in like-new working order. A buyer can expect a collector-grade vehicle that is ready for immediate enjoyment without any need for repairs or detailing.",
      "price": 49500.0,
